For each Control (Anforderung) we need:
   -The full description from the IT-Grundschutzkompendium.xml
   -The source: By default IT-Grundschutzkompendium
   -The Type: (corrective, detective, deterrent) -> ChatGPT, by using the discription as input

   -Create a Vulnerability out of the Threat -> ChatGPT

